  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2010-0283<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2010-03-11</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nWhereas the judges whose names are set out in the attached schedule have requested, with the approval of their respective Chief Justice, that they be granted leave of absence from their judicial duties from September 1, 2010 until April 30, 2011, in order to participate in the National Judicial Study Leave Fellowship Program;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nTherefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice, pursuant to subsection 54(1) of the <em>Judges Act</em>, hereby approves of leave of absence being granted to those Judges whose names are set out in the attached schedule from September 1, 2010 until April 30, 2011.\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nAttendu que les juges dont le nom figure à l’annexe ci-jointe ont demandé la permission, avec l’autorisation de leur juge en chef respectif, de prendre congé du 1<sup>er</sup> septembre 2010 au 30 avril 2011, pour participer au Programme national de bourses universitaires à l’intention des juges,\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nÀ ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice et en vertu du paragraphe 54(1) de la <em>Loi sur les juges</em>, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil autorise l’octroi d’un congé aux juges dont le nom figure à l’annexe ci-jointe pour la période allant du 1<sup>er</sup> septembre 2010 au 30 avril 2011.\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSCHEDULE\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable L. Darlene Acton\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCourt of Queen’s Bench of Alberta\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Catherine D. Aitken\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSuperior Court of Justice in and for the Province of Ontario\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Arthur M. Gans\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSuperior Court of Justice in and for the Province of Ontario\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Allan R. Hilton\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCourt of Appeal of Quebec\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Michel Richard\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSuperior Court of Quebec\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Deborah Kloegman\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSupreme Court of British Columbia\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Jean-Pierre Senécal\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSuperior Court of Quebec\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable P. Colleen Suche\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCourt of Queen’s Bench of Manitoba\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable R. James Williams\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSupreme Court of Nova Scotia\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Donna Wilson\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCourt of Queen’s Bench for Saskatchewan\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nANNEXE\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable L. Darlene Acton\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour du Banc da la Reine de l’Alberta\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Catherine D. Aitken\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour supérieure de justice de l’Ontario\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Arthur M. Gans\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour supérieure de justice de l’Ontario\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Allan R. Hilton\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour d’appel du Québec\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Michel Richard\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour supérieure du Québec\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Deborah Kloegman\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour suprême de la Colombie-Britannique\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Jean-Pierre Senécal\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour supérieure du Québec\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable P. Colleen Suche\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour du Banc de la Reine du Manitoba\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable R. James Williams\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour suprême de la Nouvelle-Écosse\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Donna Wilson\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour du Banc da la Reine de la Saskatchewan\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
